instruction: Generate a short story in less than 100 words, set in an urban city.
output: The city was bustling with life; cars, buses and people all working their way through the hustle and bustle. Jack was just another dweller in the city, trudging through his everyday transport to work. He stopped for a moment to admire the grandiose skyscrappers and vibrant lights as others hurried alongside him. He loved the life he enjoyed in this vibrant city, and hoped it would never stop.
